metadata.name: Christ the Redeemer - Rio de Janeiro
metadata.description:
The Corcovado statue, overlooking Rio de Janeiro on a very busy, sunny day in mid October 2022.  

Corcovado is a 710 meters tall mountain located in Rio de Janeiro and is home to the iconic, 38 meters tall, statue of Jesus Christ known as “Christ de Redeemer”. The mountain offers panoramic views of the city and most importantly is one of the modern Seven Wonders of the World.
